      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GALBA STACEY (4) ran well two back when hitting the frame then out of the placings at Mt Gambier latest but returns to a course where she has performed well. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. ZINFANDEL DASH (6) ran below best last time finishing fourth (31.31) over 531m at Gawler from Box 5. Has won two of two starts from this draw. Should be about the mark. KILCOY GEM (7) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a nose third (16.90) behind Binnaway Wizard at Murray Bridge. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Likely to be in the finish again. ADHANA ANNIE (3) jumps at a shorter distance and still warrants respect.",
